id.comment: Select stmt that is parent of read

query.querystr: stmt s; read r; Select s such that Parent (s, r)

id.comment: Select if statement that indirectly has while as parent

query.querystr: if ifs; while w; Select ifs such that Parent* (w, ifs)

id.comment: Select assign that has if statment indirectly as parent

query.querystr: if ifs; assign a; Select a such that Parent* (ifs, a)
